    "updated_at": "2016-10-11T21:11:55Z",
    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "I think this will fix it, but for the wrong reason. I think the real problem is that `RequiresBaseProvider` (and `Adjacency`) is set for `FACT`. Both are checked for in `BuildingInfo.IsCloseEnoughToBase`. By setting the `distanceToBaseIsImportant` argument to false, you're just avoiding this check.\n\nThe real fix will probably involve not re-using the `ChooseBuildLocation` method to get the MCV deploy location.\n"
  },
